===============================================================================
Webservice: use

@WebServiceRef(wsdlLocation = 
      "META-INF/wsdl/localhost_8080/helloservice/HelloService.wsdl")
      
Note: this code only works when running inside the server, meaning that you 
can't put that in a client app. See example where a servlet calls a webservice
at http://docs.oracle.com/javaee/6/tutorial/doc/bnayn.html
